sentence: what is the capital of the state that borders the most states ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the capital of the state that borders the most states ?
sql: select state.capital from border_info , state where state.state_name = border_info.state_name group by ( border_info.state_name ) order by count ( distinct border_info.border ) desc limit 1 ;
sql-with-vars: select state.capital from border_info , state where state.state_name = border_info.state_name group by ( border_info.state_name ) order by count ( distinct border_info.border ) desc limit 1 ;
